{"tid":512931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老唔撚識用電子野就死撚開啦","createTime":"2017-12-29T04:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T05:24:40.000Z","uid":34777,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aff4a7ffbcf8b2b3ed480fec93abe0570cc591b5","tid":512931,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"今日去入境事務署換passport <br />\n趕時間就用啲自助機諗住快啲搞掂<br />\n一見前面有個廢老用緊都心知不妙<br />\n但見有人幫諗住都應該快啦<br />\n我屌你老母 幫幫下個職員走撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住個廢老係度亂咁篤<br />\n督咗成半個鍾都未撚督完<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面成村人屌柒佢都繼續篤<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 啲廢老唔識用就乖乖地用番傳統方法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又死要面唔再叫人嚟幫又要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢老真係社會垃圾嚟 阻撚住個地球轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1681c48109df8147b1a023a3fcbaa6f91717b7e6","tid":512931,"uid":23842,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43f2e8b2480c7ec6769e3fc97f8946bfb0f6715","tid":512931,"uid":132557,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"你當面屌柒佢啦  上面屌有屁用咩鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6475942cd7acedd8584f9724dda9777a5aa1f416","tid":512931,"uid":132557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你當面屌柒佢啦  上網屌有屁用咩鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9e1fb272f609961b4ad507c45d620e099ff34787","tid":512931,"uid":22554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"其實Ｍ記Ｄ　自助機都有同一個問題<br />\n<br />\n人真係要有自知之明，　唔識用咪排番人手落單條隊囉<br />\n<br />\n又廢又唔想排隊"},{"pid":"55da5be810fa7209c222c0ef4c7e3f0ac4ae02bb","tid":512931,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你當面屌柒佢啦  上面屌有屁用咩鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有話我冇屌柒佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成村人屌柒佢</span><br />\n咁當然包埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75205a5c1e9404b56af46026a5452ffd621c3ef","tid":512931,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cae3043f4915dfad2f3a4159560bf49d8f365575","tid":512931,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解你唔幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後幫佢叫咗人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5647ec5fc20c3a7499b1600c3bceb13ccfd8edfc","tid":51293