n.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你記得去㩒錢唔好屌啲港女用得耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f110406ad2a87a9a55a5b56ff06c5dca81d950ab","tid":512931,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"有次幫人交電話費<br />\n前面條廢老唔識用自助機<br />\n即刻屌柒佢：唔識用就過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1b26bbc6d54db4898d3e8e85377a72c25af2ce","tid":512931,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次幫人交電話費<br />\n前面條廢老唔識用自助機<br />\n即刻屌柒佢：唔識用就過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次都係咁<br />\n佢大番我：我嚟先 關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54aec4135f40275599033d1c66baf8d26244fe33","tid":512931,"uid":74442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d1b26bbc6d54db4898d3e8e85377a72c25af2ce","tid":512931,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次幫人交電話費<br />\n前面條廢老唔識用自助機<br />\n即刻屌柒佢：唔識用就過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次都係咁<br />\n佢大番我：我嚟先 關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"佢唔講第二句都難駁少少<br />\n佢一講第二句就有位入<br />\n&ldquo;阻住我就關我事啦廢人&rdquo;"},{"pid":"6f4d199aa2c76f4417cf3fbc852a3a30a2892e5a","tid":512931,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有次幫人交電話費<br />\n前面條廢老唔識用自助機<br />\n即刻屌柒佢：唔識用就過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" 